Package com.kuka.geometry

This package contains interfaces and classes for the KUKA scene graph and geometry model.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    IObjectEventProvider
    Provides methods for adding or removing listeners for the event model.
    IRedundancyCollection
    Interface for holding redundancy information.
    IResourceConnector
    Connection class used to connect a scene graph object to a resource.
    IRobotFlange
    Represents a capability to obtain the flange of a robot.
    World.IValidationDelegate
    An World.IValidationDelegate is given the opportunity to prevent changes to SpatialObjects before they happen.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Frame
    A frame represents a coordinate system in three-dimensional space.
    FrameAlignmentUtils
    Utility class providing static helper methods for the frame alignment.
    FrameChain
    Represents a directed path (i.e. frame chain) between two frames connected through the frame tree.
    FrameChainElement
    A single frame chain element in the directed path from source to target frame.
    LoadData
    LoadData represents the physical load of a SpatialObject.
    LocalFrame
    This is a lightweight class that is meant for frame calculations and intermediate results.
    ObjectConnection
    Represents the connection between two spatial objects.
    ObjectEventProvider
    Event provider belonging to an object which is able to propagate events through the object tree.
    ObjectFrame
    Represents a frame that belongs to a SpatialObject.
    PhysicalObject
    Represents a real physical object that may be part of a scene graph.
    PhysicalObjectUtils
    Provides utility methods for physical objects.
    SerialKinematics
    Represents a serial kinematics that may be part of a scene graph.
    Shape
    Base class for every shape.
    SpatialObject
    Represents a geometric object that may be part of a scene graph.
    Tool
    A class used to mark objects that are used as tools in applications.
    VirtualObject
    Represents a virtual object that may be part of a scene graph.
    World
    Spatial object representing World.

Package com.kuka.geometry Description

This package contains interfaces and classes for the KUKA scene graph and geometry model.
